1
00:00:52,923 --> 00:00:54,323
De joelhos.

2
00:00:54,992 --> 00:00:56,629
Agora, droga!

3
00:01:17,723 --> 00:01:19,465
<i>OUT OF DEATH (2021)</i>

4
00:01:20,453 --> 00:01:23,934
<i>MAIS CEDO NESSE DIA...</i>

5
00:01:23,936 --> 00:01:25,930
<b><i>D3QU1NH4 | Mrs. Bennet
| LaisRosas</i></b>

6
00:01:25,932 --> 00:01:27,957
<b><i>KimLucin | Nani | Helo</i></b>

7
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:29,859
<b><i>TinTin | Rayusca</i></b>

8
00:01:29,861 --> 00:01:31,861
<b><i>Debcarda | Amand@ | anaflva</i></b>

9
00:02:30,972 --> 00:02:32,980
Este lugar parece incrível.

10
00:02:33,706 --> 00:02:35,113
